alia\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1864|1864]]\n|23 January 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Extending the mandate of [[United Nations Mission in Nepal]] until 23 July 2009\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1865|1865]]\n|27 January 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|The situation in [[C\u00f4te d'Ivoire]]\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1866|1866]]\n|13 February 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Extending mission of the [[United Nations Observer Mission in Georgia]]\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1867|1867]]\n|26 February 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Extending the [[United Nations Integrated Mission in East Timor]] until 26 February 2010\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1868|1868]]\n|23 March 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|The situation in Afghanistan. Extending [[UNAMA]] until 23 March 2010\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1869|1869]]\n|25 March 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Welcoming the new designate [[Valentin Inzko]] as [[High Representative for Bosnia and Herzegovina]] \n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1870|1870]]\n|30 April 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Extending the [[United Nations Mission in Sudan]] until 30 April 2010\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1871|1871]]\n|30 April 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Extending the [[United Nations Mission for the Referendum in Western Sahara]] until 30 April 2010\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1872|1872]]\n|26 May 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Extending the [[African Union]] Mission in Somalia ([[AMISOM]]) until 31 January 2010\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1873|1873]]\n|29 May 2009\n| 14\u20131\u20130 (against: Turkey)\n|Extending the mandate of the [[United Nations Peacekeeping Force in Cyprus]] until 15 December 2009\n|-\n|[[United Nations Security Council Resolution 1874|1874]]\n|12 June 2009\n| 15\u20130\u20130\n|Imposes further sanctions on [[North Korea]] following